#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.fillna.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.fillna"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.fillna.fillna:1 of
msgid "Fill NA/NaN values using the specified method."
msgstr "使用指定的方法填充 NA/NaN 值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.fillna.fillna of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.fillna.fillna:3 of
msgid ""
"Value to use to fill holes (e.g. 0), alternately a dict/Series/DataFrame "
"of values specifying which value to use for each index (for a Series) or "
"column (for a DataFrame).  Values not in the dict/Series/DataFrame will "
"not be filled. This value cannot be a list."
msgstr ""
"用于填充缺失值的值（例如 0），或者是一个 dict/Series/DataFrame，用于指定"
"每个索引（对于 Series）或列（对于 DataFrame）所使用的值。不在 dict/Series"
"/DataFrame 中的值将不会被填充。此值不能是列表。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.fillna.fillna:9 of
msgid ""
"Method to use for filling holes in reindexed Series pad / ffill: "
"propagate last valid observation forward to next valid backfill / bfill: "
"use next valid observation to fill gap."
msgstr ""
"用于填充重索引 Series 中缺失值的方法 pad / ffill：将最后一个有效观测值"
"向前传播到下一个有效值 backfill / bfill：使用下一个有效观测值来填充空白。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.fillna.fillna:13 of
msgid "Axis along which to fill missing values."
msgstr "用于填充缺失值的轴。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.fillna.fillna:15 of
msgid ""
"If True, fill in-place. Note: this will modify any other views on this "
"object (e.g., a no-copy slice for a column in a DataFrame)."
msgstr ""
"如果为 True，则就地填充。注意：这将修改该对象上的任何其他视图（例如，"
"DataFrame 中某一列的无复制切片）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.fillna.fillna:19 of
msgid ""
"If method is specified, this is the maximum number of consecutive NaN "
"values to forward/backward fill. In other words, if there is a gap with "
"more than this number of consecutive NaNs, it will only be partially "
"filled. If method is not specified, this is the maximum number of entries"
" along the entire axis where NaNs will be filled. Must be greater than 0 "
"if not None."
msgstr ""
"如果指定了方法，则这是向前/向后填充连续 NaN 值的最大数量。换句话说，如果"
"存在超过此数量的连续 NaN 缺失，则只会被部分填充。如果未指定方法，则这是沿"
"整个轴 NaN 将被填充的最大条目数。如果不为 None，则必须大于 0。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.fillna.fillna:26 of
msgid ""
"A dict of item->dtype of what to downcast if possible, or the string "
"'infer' which will try to downcast to an appropriate equal type (e.g. "
"float64 to int64 if possible)."
msgstr ""
"一个 dict，表示如果可能的话要向下转换的项目->数据类型，或者字符串 'infer'"
"，它将尝试向下转换为合适的相等类型（例如，如果可能的话，将 float64 转换为"
" int64）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.fillna.fillna of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.fillna.fillna:31 of
msgid "Object with missing values filled or None if ``inplace=True``."
msgstr "填充了缺失值的对象，如果 ``inplace=True`` 则返回 None。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.fillna.fillna of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.fillna.fillna:36 of
msgid ":py:obj:`interpolate`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.fillna.fillna:37 of
msgid "Fill NaN values using interpolation."
msgstr "使用插值填充 NaN 值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.fillna.fillna:39 of
msgid ":py:obj:`reindex`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.fillna.fillna:40 of
msgid "Conform object to new index."
msgstr "使对象符合新的索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.fillna.fillna:42 of
msgid ":py:obj:`asfreq`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.fillna.fillna:43 of
msgid "Convert TimeSeries to specified frequency."
msgstr "将时间序列转换为指定频率。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.fillna.fillna:46 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.fillna.fillna:61 of
msgid "Replace all NaN elements with 0s."
msgstr "将所有 NaN 元素替换为 0。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.fillna.fillna:70 of
msgid "We can also propagate non-null values forward or backward."
msgstr "我们也可以将非空值向前或向后传播。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.fillna.fillna:79 of
msgid ""
"Replace all NaN elements in column 'A', 'B', 'C', and 'D', with 0, 1, 2, "
"and 3 respectively."
msgstr "将列 'A'、'B'、'C' 和 'D' 中的所有 NaN 元素分别替换为 0、1、2 和 3。"

